<sect1 id="dir_9144a23a4f464d408d92b5f36620fa56_1autotoc_md114">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::spawn::commands</title><para>Commands for spawn and despawn operations.</para>
<para>This namespace contains command classes that represent spawn and despawn requests. These commands are emitted by systems and processed by dispatchers during the command flush phase.</para>
</sect1>
