</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>SpawnCommand</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Requests spawning of GameObjects from a pool  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>DespawnCommand</computeroutput>  </para>
